test_even_range:
assert [86, 88] == [176, 178, 180]
  At index 0 diff: 86 != 176
  Right contains one more item: 180
  Full diff:
  - [176, 178, 180]
  + [86, 88]
test_large_range:
assert [86, 87, 88, 89] == [88, 89, 90]
  At index 0 diff: 86 != 88
  Left contains one more item: 89
  Full diff:
  - [88, 89, 90]
  + [86, 87, 88, 89]
